"N$10003" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "REPORDEM"."STATE" , "REPORDEM"."PARTY" , "REPORDEM"."TOTAL_VOTES_CAST" , "FCHARITIES"."FOUNDATION" , "FCHARITIES"."STATE" "STATE1" , "FCHARITIES"."SORT_NAME" , "FCHARITIES"."AFFILIATION" , "FCHARITIES"."ACTIVITY" , "FCHARITIES"."STREET" , "FCHARITIES"."STATUS" , "FCHARITIES"."RULING" , "FCHARITIES"."PF_FILING_REQ_CD" , "FCHARITIES"."ZIP" , "FCHARITIES"."ORGANIZATION" , "FCHARITIES"."INCOME_AMT" , "FCHARITIES"."CLASSIFICATION" , "FCHARITIES"."SUBSECTION" , "FCHARITIES"."ASSET_AMT" , "FCHARITIES"."EIN" , "FCHARITIES"."FILING_REQ_CD" , "FCHARITIES"."NAME" , "FCHARITIES"."ACCT_PD" , "FCHARITIES"."NTEE_CD" , "FCHARITIES"."ASSET_CD" , "FCHARITIES"."INCOME_CD" , "FCHARITIES"."WEALTH" , "FCHARITIES"."REVENUE_AMT" , "FCHARITIES"."ASS" , "FCHARITIES"."ICO" , "FCHARITIES"."CITY" , "FCHARITIES"."DEDUCTIBILITY" , "FCHARITIES"."TAX_PERIOD"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE:10013} "REPORDEM"
INNER JOIN {INPUT_SOURCE:10017} "FCHARITIES" ON "REPORDEM"."STATE" = "FCHARITIES"."STATE" )
